#: ../../../HIPSupport.rst:46
msgid ""
"CPUs: HIP support is available through the HIP-CPU runtime library `<https://"
"github.com/ROCm/HIP-CPU>`_. This header-only library enables CPUs to execute "
"unmodified HIP code."
msgstr ""

