#: ../../../HIPSupport.rst:574
msgid ""
"`Exceptions <https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/exceptions>`_ cannot "
"be used by the user provided callable;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../HIPSupport.rst:576
msgid ""
"Dynamic memory allocation (e.g. ``operator new``) cannot be used by the user "
"provided callable;"
